column2: SELECT TOP #     DISTINCT(artist.Name),     artist.ArtistId,     COUNT(Track.AlbumId) AS Num_tracks,     SUM(Track.UnitPrice) As Price FROM chinook.Album album INNER JOIN chinook.Track track ON album.AlbumId = track.AlbumId INNER JOIN chinook.Artist artist ON album.ArtistId = artist.ArtistId GROUP BY artist.Name, album.AlbumId, artist.ArtistId ORDER BY SUM(Track.UnitPrice) DESC
